snippet.title: Tres RELEASE trailer | AUGUST 12
snippet.description:
THE GAME IS OUT NOW! With a limited time offer for you to play with your friends.

Yea I couldn't make a serious trailer :P

Tres is a cards-based game where you, with another player, have to compete againt each other to see wich one is the first to put on the table all of their cards.

STEAM PAGE OUT NOW! https://store.steampowered.com/app/3120160/Tres/
